  • public class StockGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Zaine Ashe - 09469010 A class that generates a random stock for use in testing

    Used for TruckTest.java and ManifestTest.java where trucks need to be filled with stock before testing each classes functionality. Placed into it's own class for neatness's sake.
